aa(lp108
VWhat I've been doing at MoMA since the beginning is to try to
p109
aVharness the power of MoMA
p110
aVbecause it's great to work there. You really have power
p111
aVin that people usually tend to know about your exhibition or see the exhibitions,
p112
aVand that is power because in a design museum I wouldn't have as many visitors.
