p114
aVand then they stumble upon my show and I keep them there.
p115
aa(lp116
VBut what I've been trying to do is something that the curators at MoMA
p117
aVin my department have been doing ever since the museum was founded in 1929,
p118
aVwhich is to try and see what's going on in the world
p119
aVand try to use that authority in order to make things better.
